    Object oPageHeader_DD is a cPageHeaderDataDictionary
        Set DDO_Server To oEmployee_DD
        Set DDO_Server To oLine_DD
        Property Date pdStartdate
        Property Date pdStopdate

        Procedure OnConstrain 
            Date dStart dStop

            Get pdStartdate To dStart
            Get pdStopdate To dStop

            Case Begin
                Case (dStart <> 0 and dStop <> 0)
                    Constrain PageHeader.date between dStart and dStop
                    Case Break
                Case (dStart <> 0)
                    Constrain PageHeader.date GE dStart
                    Case Break
                Case (dStop <> 0)
                    Constrain PageHeader.date LE dStop
            Case End
        End_Procedure 
    End_Object 

